content: 12 make sure everything is stuffed properly round 3 decrease 2 st x6 6 ℅ and use the tail to close any gaps you may have between the balls your willy is now finished if you wish to add a little blush effect to the cheeks just mix a bit of fabric paint with water and apply with a small paintbrush photos on next page be sure to test the saturation on a piece of paper towel or even some scrap yarn before applying to your finished amigurumi designed and written by crystal mihaylo pickrel - not your nana s yarnwork - 2019 - all rights reserved 6 winston the willy pattern send me your dick pics i really hope you enjoyed this pattern and that you love your finished winston- please be sure to tag any photos of your finished willies at @notyournanasyarnwork on instagram if you have any questions regarding this pattern feel free to contact me at crystalpickrelonetsy@yahoo com​ and if you really loved this pattern and you want to show your appreciation + fuel my creativity for future patterns you can send me a cup of coffee on ko-fi ko-fi com/notyournanasyarnwork designed and written by crystal mihaylo pickrel - not your nana s yarnwork - 2019 - all rights reserved 7
